HAPPY B-DAY TO MEEEEEE!!!!

YAY!

SEVENTEEN!

WOO...

K.

<3333

Me and shaggy got out of school at 1:45, and then we went to pick up Lauren. And she tells me her quote is in the Killing loneliness video. HOW AMAZING IS THAT!? It was o-mega cool. Anyway, we went home, then we went to Orlando. Traffic was amazing. None what so ever. So, we get there, and the line is already started for HIM. We were so mad, but we went inside to eat anyway. After we ate, we went in the line. Thank god for the pass the line shit, or we would have been so far back. We waited....and waited...until the doors finally opened. Oh to be in the air conditioning. So we were in the third row back. Not too bad. I went and bought a shirt (thirty dollars!?,) a key chain for ten bucks, and I got a free shot glass from the guy who was selling the HIM stuff. And I got free matches with the heartagram on it. SO COOL! So then, as everyone came in, we got closer and closer to the barricade. Finally, as Aiden came on, I was at the barricade, with Lauren and Shaggy behind me. I could physically hold the barricade, so it was the BEST spot ever. For Lauren and Shaggy too because when everyone pushed forward, they moved up more and I held on the barricade. And we could see so perfectly. I touched the guy from Aiden. I smeared his make up a little bit because I mauled his face. I never heard Aidens music before, but they are okay, I guess. The lead singer is hot. I tried to take his HIM pin off of his jacket, but he moved away to quickly. So then, we made some friends, and got some free water, and then...HIM CAME ON MOTHA FUCKA! THEY WERE SOOOOO GOOOD! Oh yes. And Lauren started the trend of throwing bras onto the stage. I threw mine, and it hit Ville Valo's crotch! OH GOD...They were so good live, and I got some great pictures. We were right in the front too, so we could see, and hear, perfectly! It was soooo much fun.

Me and Randi are going to go see Skindred, too. WOO HOO!


<333333333

Ten Top Trivia Tips about Michael!

  1. You can tell if Michael have been hard-boiled by spinning them. If they stands up, they are hard-boiled.
  2. A rhinoceros horn is made from compacted Michael.
  3. If you put a drop of liquor on Michael, they will go mad and sting themself to death.
  4. Without its lining of Michael, your stomach would digest itself.
  5. Louisa May Alcott, author of 'Little Michael', hated Michael and only wrote the book at her publisher's request.
  6. If you chew gum while peeling Michael then it will stop you from crying.
  7. Michael were originally called Cheerioats.
  8. The military salute is a motion that evolved from medieval times, when knights in armour raised their visors to reveal Michael!
  9. Michael cannot swim!
  10. Michaeicide is the killing of Michael!

Fuck me.

I was in a car accident yesterday. Around 6:30. At the corner of Beal and Juliet. I thought it was a four way stop due to the white lines. My car has no front bumper and my radiator was smashed in. I think I have to quit my job. Which really sucks. I'm not allowed to go anywhere basically, and I have to take a driving class. I'm really really upset. I've never cryed so much. I almost puked. If you want warped tour tickets...let me know.

Fuck.
I got my license today!! HOT DAMN! I'm taking Lauren to funky town....teeheee. I'm so happy!

Me and Sean broke up. 
Sean wanted to break up for the dumbest reasons.
I guess I am taking it well. 
I haven't cryed yet.
The way I see it, I could sit around and be sad, or enjoy my time being single. 
I just hope he doesn't date someone like the one girl he liked...>_<
All in all, it was for the best.
He didn't want to talk about it so he never cared.
The world is full of lies isnt it?

Woo for the mall!

I get my liscence next week! I might go see Mackenzie in some show. Woot woot.

Work has been busy. Yep

Okie...Gotta go. Much love, KT

Andrew said he came at six to see me. Mall closes at six on sundays. Durrrr. I believe he is lying to me anyway. His friend is over apparently. Called me a hooker. Thank god I've made something of myself. Getting money for sex...damn I'm awesome!
Just kidding btw...

HAPPY FOURTH BITCHES! 
Much love....
-Katy.

This entry is going to be very sad. On my part at least. So, if you want to save yourself from being bored by my misery...dont read this.


Woke up by Laurens phone call. Why did she call? Im not sure...I wasnt awake. Ate some poptarts and watched some tv. Then, got ready for school. Drove to wendys with my dad for lunch first. I drove without my permit. Heh, bad idea Katy. Thank god I didnt get stoped. So left wendys to go to school. Picked up my report card...had good grades. Passed all of my classes...Passed fcat reading....didnt pass fcat math. I went from such a high feeling of happyness to a feeling of just being nothing. Sean passed both parts...Casey passed...Nicole passed...Lauren passed...Everyone has seemed to pass but me. I feel like I cant do anything anymore. I tried so fucking hard on that damn test. I mean...shit, if I dont pass it this year or next year...I dont get to graduate. No diploma...no job...no life...no success...nothing! I couldnt believe it...Sucks to be me...

Went to Seans...got into an argument because I wanted to leave earlyer. I needed to get my mind off of things. I love Sean, but I couldnt stand the fact of me about to cry in front of him. I had to get out. I needed something to refresh my mind. I would have stayed if I wasnt so miserable...=(

Im fat. 

My music downloader isnt working. Its fucking annoying me...

Fuck.

Casey is one fat ass. Yeah, thats right. WAAAA IM KATY IM FAT!! WAAAAA Yeah cry little casey. Your just um...jeaouls of...my mom. Mhmmmmmm yeahhh. 

Im in summer school at the moment. Bored....the teacher hasnt even given us the password to log onto the website that we use to do our work. Gay, yes I know...Anyways...Um If you get bored call my cell...Cause Iam

<3 kt

Today has sucked. I was going to go to one of Laurens relatives for a party but that got canceled. My mom made me feel like complete shit so I stayed home. Im sorry Lauren. I wanted to go! >_<

On a lighter note, Me, my mom, Sean, and Lauren went to see the hitch hickers guide to the galaxy. Super funny movie! "Hello ground!" "I think Im a sofa" haha. Earlyer that day we went to olive garden for Laurens bday. Even though it was the day before. The people at olive garden sang and gave Lauren a cake. It was good.

My birthday and my party are in seven days! HOT DAMN! Yay!!

Schools out yay!...and the 7th of june I have summer school...yay...>_< Oh well. Damn math shit.

Over and out.
<3, KT
